{"tid":1758937,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"汪洋要求重新解釋所有宗教教義、教規","createTime":"2019-11-27T10:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T13:59:57.000Z","uid":240448,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3ba7e5ae212528524b3bb509fde7804984615897","tid":1758937,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T10:59:46.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】全國政協主席汪洋要求，所有宗教要以社會主義核心價值觀重新解釋教義、教規。有分析認為，中共這樣做，是要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">加強整頓地下教會，以至是新疆穆斯林</span></strong></span>。 <br />\n<br />\n汪洋在北京出席全國政協民族和宗教委員會的座談會，他強調教義、教規的解釋是重要基礎工作，各個宗教要深入學習領會中共總書記習近平的重要論述，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">逐步形成具有中國特色、符合時代發展要求的宗教思想體系，落實宗教與社會主義社會相適應的思想基礎</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n十六名宗教界政協委員和專家學者等認同重新解釋教義、教規，是宗教中國化、時代化的歷史選擇，需要重視的是，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">目前成果比較零散、解釋不夠系統深入、缺乏高水平人才等，又認為與時並進，權威準確解釋經典教義，有效抵禦極端思想、異端邪說侵蝕</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n中共總書記習近平在2016年的宗教工作會議定調，既要堅持宗教信仰自由，也要依法管理宗教事務，又堅持政教分離，所<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有宗教不得干預行政、司法、教育等職能實施，另外又要堅決抵禦境外的宗教滲透，防範極端思想侵害。所以官方只是承認天主教愛國會的地位，和打壓地下教會</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">其中對新疆的整頓力度最強，爭議也最大，例如禁止伊斯蘭教的泛清真化，改變他們的生活習慣，不可以只吃清真食品。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約時報》最新披露多份中國政府治理新疆的機密文件，當中有習近平的內部講話，有分析認為，如果文件屬實，確認了習近平扭轉新疆危局的關鍵作用，同時揭露他對宗教極端思想的個人看法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52b3f6f8c338a0aa3626582b928829361bc43ae5","tid":1758937,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:02:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=371467&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D371467%26refer%3DShare&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRLTyP%2F9hhZoMZuVNmYF6dao%3D&h=0be2664c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D371467%26refer%3DShare&h=b3c10e7f\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=371467&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"fdb7c169e6b67df0d34df7a0c19bb7cfae0b6bb3","tid":1758937,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:02:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mr4X8aB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMr4X8aB.png&h=8a1e5102&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5063894a19866c3f1304cbb15adc05c340d3b5dd","tid":1758937,"uid":156509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:04:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">今日新疆 明日香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"de7f09fec246b0a2978e35ecec323f87927e757c","tid":1758937,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:05:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><strong>今日新疆 明日香港</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"850da60fae6a596c6dc00c36517193b2e761a3f7","tid":1758937,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:06:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><strong>今日新疆 明日香港</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b93e45187b525cea2d9a7900ddc76f531efe8860","tid":1758937,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:08:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><strong>今日新疆 明日香港</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"e84eb1ea579384df852abbed06e258b59515da3f","tid":1758937,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:38:35.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"debdcd4710d868f79c7213f04a4d4e1451cfefa0","tid":1758937,"uid":240448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019